  <ns0:data key="d1">deliverable</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Gfe Procurement Request facilitates acquisition of government furnished equipment and is required as needed for X002 and X003 under section 4.B.5.a.(i).</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d3">chunk-aa9424078fa723e2caaae8aa59fb4397</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d4">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
