  <ns0:data key="d1">deliverable</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Navy Watercraft Production Schedule guides the timing and execution of maintenance, testing, and delivery tasks for Navy Watercraft.&lt;SEP&gt;Navy Watercraft Production Schedule outlines production timelines for watercraft and is required not later than the WDC-III for the respective production period for X002 under section 6.F.3.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d3">chunk-aa9424078fa723e2caaae8aa59fb4397&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6887833d0f1a6398bb6c8fd6f72d5c8</ns0:data>
