  <ns0:data key="d2">Missing, Lost, Stolen, Broken, Damaged Or Unusable Navy Property/Government Furnished Equipment Report notifies of property issues and is required within three business days via email and 15 days for full written report for X002 under section 6.A.3.d.</ns0:data>
