  <ns0:data key="d1">document</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Signed Statement must be furnished with the offer if the offeror deletes or modifies subparagraph (a)(2) of the provision, setting forth the circumstances of the disclosure in detail.</ns0:data>
