<ns0:node id="Earned Value Management">
  <ns0:data key="d0">Earned Value Management</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d1">concept</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Earned Value Management concepts and principles are incorporated into MCMC's methodology and techniques for managing associated costs and schedules, though certification is not required.&lt;SEP&gt;Earned Value Management is defined by the acronym EVM.&lt;SEP&gt;Earned Value Management includes Planned Value, Earned Value, Actual Cost reporting, and Estimate At Completion (EAC) Projections for USMC and Navy ACRNs and individual Task Orders.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d3">chunk-bee5e6b5db1fe2dc611fc5fc2b227a51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-46778545759b6a3b0240557a9acb9577&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-939c604b9027c9cc38a7fb31f4c86c29</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d4">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d5">1759841078</ns0:data>
