  <ns0:data key="d1">technology</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Marine Corps Enterprise Network is a government-owned, government-operated enterprise network supported by MCMC for managed and sustainment services.&lt;SEP&gt;Marine Corps Enterprise Network is defined by the acronym MCEN.</ns0:data>
