<ns0:node id="Marine Corps Maintenance Contractor">
  <ns0:data key="d0">Marine Corps Maintenance Contractor</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d1">organization</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">The Marine Corps Maintenance Contractor provides logistics services including maintenance, supply management, and support for prepositioned assets.&lt;SEP&gt;Marine Corps Maintenance Contractor is defined by the acronym MCMC.</ns0:data>
