<ns0:node id="Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island">
  <ns0:data key="d0">Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d1">location</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island is the Jacksonville, Florida-based facility where primary logistics work, including maintenance and supply operations, is conducted.&lt;SEP&gt;Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island is defined by the acronym MCSF BI.&lt;SEP&gt;Marine Corps Support Facility Blount Island (MCSF-BI) occupies the eastern half of Blount Island and manages access for visitors.</ns0:data>
