<ns0:node id="Other Logistics Support">
  <ns0:data key="d0">Other Logistics Support</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d1">concept</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">Other Logistics Support requires MCMC to provide contingency, exercise, and emerging requirements support in accordance with the Statement of Work, priced as CPFF on an hours basis with overtime premium not subject to fee and fixed fee determined per Section H-8.3.&lt;SEP&gt;Cost Plus Fixed Fee hours for contingency, exercise, and emerging requirements support per the Statement of Work, with overtime premium not subject to fee.&lt;SEP&gt;Other Logistics Support is defined by the acronym OLS.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d3">chunk-46778545759b6a3b0240557a9acb9577&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f0bef8ac155e28eb1ccd0095250383c3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f6510cadeb544a78c12488882601935c</ns0:data>
