  <ns0:data key="d1">document</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">IRS Form 941 is used for reconciling total payroll to total labor costs distribution.&lt;SEP&gt;Irs Form 941 reconciles total payroll to labor costs in indirect cost rate proposals.</ns0:data>
