  <ns0:data key="d3">chunk-5fcb066f3ce0c1cfffc65441135b96e1</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d2">MCMC configures and prepositions the Arrival and Assembly Support Package as directed by the government-provided AASP Plan, consisting of materials for containerized asset issue outside MAGTF Table of Equipment.</ns0:data>
