  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC provides operational, fiscal, and logistical support to Navy, including participation in meetings and maintenance of situational awareness.&lt;SEP&gt;Navy receives planning, estimating, safety, environmental compliance, and logistics support from MCMC for operations and maintenance.</ns0:data>
