</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="NAV-P" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">11.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC submits reports, requests, and notifications to NAV-P for approvals, status updates, and directions on GFE, vehicles, and fiscal matters.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC notifies NAV-P of issues like system unavailability or asset discrepancies and seeks approvals for adjustments and requisitions.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC coordinates with NAV-P for approvals, submissions, and remedies in logistics operations.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC coordinates with NAV-P for maintenance, delivers logs and reports, and seeks approvals for shortages and repairs.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC notifies NAV-P within one hour of emergent repair identifications and submits various reports like Corrosion Survey Reports and Maintenance Status Reports for review and approval.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC provides data entry, procurement, and support services to NAV-P for external contracts and watercraft systems.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC submits schedules, reports, and records to NAV-P within specified timelines and upon request within one business day.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC submits reports, requests approvals, and provides documentation such as CDRLs to NAV-P for Navy Watercraft tasks.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC notifies NAV-P Department Director for non-operational GSE and accidents.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC notifies NAV-P of scheduled WHE inspections and tests at least five business days prior, and of accidents and near misses per timelines in NAVFAC P-307.&lt;SEP&gt;NAV-P provides technical direction to MCMC and receives maintenance reports and accident forms for CESE.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">approval,coordination,inspection scheduling,notification,notification protocol,oversight,report receipt,reporting,request response,requirement fulfillment,service provision,submission</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-955c2fafc0e5a2a07e97130b42a872b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f808346dbf233cd47e4c673a7cf87022&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d6887833d0f1a6398bb6c8fd6f72d5c8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5edf02307c6ad1788f6967955fbea6ff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2bae9a24e71825050f79fc141b2e181&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85b50b451f72c11f155dc39b516d8dd3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e151c7682b4ed7c6cd2fcdc2e29ec22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93c4a54422e967728929a60f73e593e2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e73c8ab3a0b248cdeedb8496a5c6f8a9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4c2c73655d1d9f038ea8945f49a05a1f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7659b0abfc62a3f8f0edbf4a1fee058e</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841135</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
