<ns0:edge source="Government Furnished Equipment (GFE)" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">3.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC maintains accountability, cleanliness, and serviceability of Navy GFE using DPAS and reports any issues within specified timelines.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC performs maintenance, repair, and self-help on Government Furnished Equipment as delineated in the SOW.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC performs PMCS and CM on Organic GFE and Non-PO equipment in accordance with CmdO 4790.1, MCO 4790.2, MCO 4790.25, and applicable TMs.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">corrective actions,maintenance,management,preventive maintenance,utilization</ns0:data>
