  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC follows NAVSUP P-485 for supply chain management, including replenishment, disposal, and storage of Navy materiel.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC conducts reconciliations, receipt validations, and maintains audit trails in line with NAVSUP P-485 procedures.</ns0:data>
