</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="MCO 4400.201" target="MMV200 General Account">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MMV200 General Account serves as the first source for requisitions in accordance with MCO 4400.201.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">requisition guidance,supply sourcing</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-68739860c42b764e52f9649ea16ed702</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841185</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="MCO 4400.201" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">8.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC conducts validations, reconciliations, and issue management in accordance with MCO 4400.201.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC follows MCO 4400.201 for establishing physical locations for On-Island, Shipboard, and MCPP-PHIL DSIs.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC conducts inventories and maintains accountability in accordance with MCO 4400.201.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC conducts SL-3 inventories and requisitions in accordance with MCO 4400.201.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC performs Class VIII management and sustainment in accordance with MCO 4400.201 (Vol. 12).&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC follows MCO 4400.201 for conducting COSIS, maintaining databases, P3&amp;M, security, notifications, and inventory adjustments.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC provides SECREP support in accordance with MCO 4400.201 during MPF exercises.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC conducts cyclic inventories in compliance with MCO 4400.201 to reconcile intermediate supply accounts during transition.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">compliance,compliance guideline,guidance adherence,inventory compliance,inventory management,management,policy adherence,procedural compliance,procedural guidance,procedures,storage procedures,supply support</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-abd2ceb311ce78c8a8c1fe38d11ee4f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67bad1bd73dd9a9a7549acb855ae5e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f17f0fbf6c678da23e588ab57f6900&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a136ea2c9ab7ea9bb718fd0abd010d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22de15a10ae9bfba6096cca855d5f78a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68739860c42b764e52f9649ea16ed702&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65833c099ebcc7aa1fccc5a1d930a7aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0a00a7bb666b381893da579a6b228c9</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841206</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="MCO 4400.201" target="DSI">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Demand-Supported Items are managed in accordance with MCO 4400.201 for stockage criteria and storage.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">compliance,inventory management</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-89b1a9fa6c0722adcd478e665df09141</ns0:data>
