  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The Defense Federal Acquisition Regulation Supplement builds on the Federal Acquisition Regulation by specifying thresholds for clause inclusion in subcontracts.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">supplemental regulation,threshold specification</ns0:data>
