  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Federal Acquisition Regulation clause 52.216-8 governs fixed fee payments in Cost Plus Fixed Fee task orders, expressed in dollars and subject to scope adjustments.</ns0:data>
