<ns0:edge source="Contractor" target="Government">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The Contractor fully cooperates with Government investigations and awaits Government determination for operator resumption after incidents.&lt;SEP&gt;The Contractor provides assistance and cooperation for Government-conducted audits, evaluations, and inspections of equipment.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">approval process,assistance,compliance,oversight</ns0:data>
