  <ns0:data key="d7">Contractor, as prime, is responsible for settling subcontractor amounts and rates in the completion invoice or voucher.&lt;SEP&gt;The Contractor shall insert equal opportunity clause terms into subcontracts with subcontractors valued above specified FAR thresholds and enforce compliance as directed.</ns0:data>
