  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841336</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="GFP" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC is responsible for maintaining GFP in operable condition, including repairs, and ensuring its use only for contract performance.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">custodial maintenance,property management</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-f736781b685dec5629d8433e71c666e4</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841145</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="GFP" target="Successor">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The Successor assumes control and accountability for GFP from the Incumbent as of the date the Government accepts the joint inventory.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">accountability transfer,inventory acceptance</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-b6f17f0fbf6c678da23e588ab57f6900</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841369</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="BICmd" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">8.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC manages multiple accounts at BICmd, including intermediate and consumer levels across dispersed locations.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC and BICmd jointly use QMSS for quality management and share access to reports for sustainment and operations.&lt;SEP&gt;BICmd provides guidance, direction, and oversight to MCMC as the Executive Agent for MCPP.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC jointly participates with BICmd Government representatives in annual RIP recomputations and inventory efforts.&lt;SEP&gt;BICmd prescribes specific sub-inventories for sustainment blocks on ships other than T-AKEs.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC delivers SF153 to the BICmd KMI manager for KMI asset transfers during exercises.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC is jointly certified with BICmd under ISO 9001:2015 during scheduled surveillance.&lt;SEP&gt;#&gt;|MCMC provides voice, video, and data services in support of BICmd at Blount Island.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">account management,asset transfer,coordination,documentation,inventory support,joint certification,joint operations,joint participation,operational continuity,operational scope,oversight,service support,sub-inventory prescription,sustainment blocks</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-67bad1bd73dd9a9a7549acb855ae5e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c12bdd730383e0d5968b0354d37c6d8a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8efbcbadad92a347ffdc7b5c1e34b2f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93752a7bd8aca85ef0ce5fea3701dc32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf666a8ded534eb47b7eede4412a01f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68739860c42b764e52f9649ea16ed702&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d0f24c6dd1ff5486bfe7491203ea801&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93c4a54422e967728929a60f73e593e2</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841152</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="BICmd" target="KMI">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">BICmd manages the KMI account for COMSEC/CCI assets and provides concurrence on MCMC appointments and transfers.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">account management,oversight</ns0:data>
