<ns0:edge source="MCO P4400.151" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC adheres to MCO P4400.151 for receipt management, consumables procurement, and SECREP requisitioning.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC manages physical inventory of MPE/S in accordance with MCO P4400.151.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">MPE/S management,compliance,logistics procedures</ns0:data>
