<ns0:edge source="Blount Island Command" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC personnel adhere to Blount Island Command's security instructions, orders, and directives while on site.&lt;SEP&gt;Blount Island Command collaborates with MCMC on QMSS KPI reporting and MMC performance reviews.&lt;SEP&gt;Blount Island Command determines facility closures for foul weather and directs MCMC personnel departures or preparations.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC utilizes Blount Island Command resources for personnel deployment and maintenance in support of exercises as per Exercise Support Letter.</ns0:data>
