<ns0:edge source="Government" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC provides investigation reports, forms, and requests to the Government for review and approval in accordance with specified procedures and timelines.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC nominates custodians and personnel in writing to the Government and provides various reports like CDRL 5044 and CDRL 5045.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC submits inventory results and reports to the Government within specified timelines.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC submits reports and nominations to the Government for approval and review.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">approval,approval process,compliance,nomination,reporting</ns0:data>
