  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC conducts weapons SL-3 inventory and replenishment IAW Section 4.B with Government oversight.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">procedural guidance,weapon SL-3</ns0:data>
