  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Link-Belt Rough Terrain Crane is assigned Priority 1 maintenance under GSE for lifting operations.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">criticality,priority assignment</ns0:data>
