<ns0:edge source="ISO 9001" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC auditors are certified to ISO 9001 and participate in related Joint Management Reviews.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC develops and implements local procedures in accordance with ISO 9001 for timely and accurate data provision in business systems.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC implements local procedures per ISO 9001 for timely and accurate data.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC develops and implements local procedures in accordance with ISO 9001 for timely and accurate data provision.</ns0:data>
