<ns0:edge source="Navy CESE" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC ensures Navy CESE is evenly planned and distributed in the production plan, balanced with USMC equipment for timely completion.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC executes temporary loans of Navy CESE to operating forces during exercises or contingencies, adjusting the Consolidated Asset Listing (CAL) accordingly.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">equipment loaning,equipment planning,workload balance</ns0:data>
