<ns0:edge source="Letter of Non-Conformance" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">3.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC submits Letter of Non-Conformance to COR for any deviations from schedule or milestones within 5 business days.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC submits a Letter of Non-Conformance for each item not completed and ready for FMC by the baseline finish date.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC issues a Letter of Non-Conformance for any non-FMC functional areas at the end of Phase D Stage 4, detailing mitigation efforts to meet delivery requirements.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">capability reporting,completion status,deviation handling,reporting requirement,submission</ns0:data>
