<ns0:edge source="OEM" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC maintains equipment and performs certifications following OEM recommendations and standards.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC procures parts and follows manuals from OEM for load bearing and safety devices.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC procures WHE load bearing, load controlling, and operational safety devices from OEM per NAVFAC P-307.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC procures all WHE load bearing parts, load controlling parts, and operational safety devices from OEM as per NAVFAC P-307 examples.</ns0:data>
