<ns0:edge source="MHE" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">3.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC manages personnel training, testing, and licensing for MHE in support of warehousing and distribution operations.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC includes MHE in vehicle and equipment operations, dispatch, and operator training.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC ensures MHE used for suspended loads meets NAVFAC P-307 requirements.</ns0:data>
