<ns0:edge source="SL-3" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC conducts SL-3 inventory on ME and CESE during maintenance induction and ensures components meet prepositioning shelf life criteria.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC performs SL-3 inventories and requisitions deficiencies to meet production and backload timelines.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC maintains chain of custody for SL-3 during repairs and modifications of ME.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC inventories SL-3 annually during PMCS and stores it securely in accordance with stowage configurations.</ns0:data>
