<ns0:edge source="CmdO 4790.1" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC conducts supply and maintenance reconciliations in accordance with CmdO 4790.1.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC performs PMCS and CM on Organic GFE in accordance with CmdO 4790.1 (MMSOP) and related orders.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC follows CmdO 4790.1 for PMCS, CM, special maintenance actions, and other programs like C3 and cannibalization.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC conducts and documents supply and maintenance reconciliations in accordance with CmdO 4790.1.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">GFE maintenance,PMCS guidance,compliance,documentation,maintenance guidance,procedural guidance</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-13a4841aefad66042f059edb023e607b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-955c2fafc0e5a2a07e97130b42a872b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68739860c42b764e52f9649ea16ed702&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5e151c7682b4ed7c6cd2fcdc2e29ec22</ns0:data>
