<ns0:edge source="GCSS-MC" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">17.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC uses GCSS-MC to process confirmations of receipt, requisitions, and issuances for materiel.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC uses GCSS-MC for supply transactions, requisitions, obligations, and daily reconciliations.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC uploads PMCS records and forms to GCSS-MC for accountability and inventory management.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC uses GCSS-MC Planner's Desktop to manage min-max for Shipboard and MCPP-PHIL DSIs and ensure data accuracy.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC completes supply transactions and adjustments in GCSS-MC for inventory discrepancies and monthly field changes.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC identifies corrective maintenance via GCSS-MC service requests and enters NDT results, PMCS records, and inspections.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC utilizes GCSS-MC for recording and reporting maintenance and supply efforts in support of MCPP logistics functions.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC updates GCSS-MC based on SOUM and MAM, and uses it for DSI min-max management and parts validation.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC uses GCSS-MC to record tasks, notes, and documentation for maintenance activities on managed equipment.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC uses GCSS-MC for uploading documents, managing sub-inventories, and reflecting temporary loan status.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC uses GCSS-MC for requisitions and operations while Government approves to avoid IGF of fund obligation.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC records services, filter replacements, and SL-3 components in GCSS-MC as separate tasks under service requests.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC uses GCSS-MC to ensure accurate SECREP condition codes and to upload packages for disposition requests.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC records maintenance services and PMCS tasks as separate entries in GCSS-MC.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC utilizes GCSS-MC to document maintenance services on IT assets, including uploads of external requisitions and debriefs of labor and materials.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC records PMCS actions, fuel filter services, and equipment status updates in GCSS-MC, including ABD SHIP placements and additions to the Deferred Maintenance Listing (DML).&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC uses GCSS-MC to record PMCS actions, recoil exercises, and lubricity fuel filter services for EBFL.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">accountability management,approval role,asset tracking,compliance,data management,documentation,inventory management,logistics recording,logistics support,maintenance documentation,reconciliation,record upload,recording,reporting,service recording,service requests,system integration,system updates,system utilization,task documentation,transaction processing,utilization</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-955c2fafc0e5a2a07e97130b42a872b5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-13a4841aefad66042f059edb023e607b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67bad1bd73dd9a9a7549acb855ae5e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-48caa545ec007aaf46c9abe9ec8c0c78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8efbcbadad92a347ffdc7b5c1e34b2f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8a136ea2c9ab7ea9bb718fd0abd010d4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cf666a8ded534eb47b7eede4412a01f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-68739860c42b764e52f9649ea16ed702&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65833c099ebcc7aa1fccc5a1d930a7aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd3a05bb896b89de7fd366c654ad4a6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d0f24c6dd1ff5486bfe7491203ea801&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89b1a9fa6c0722adcd478e665df09141&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bee5e6b5db1fe2dc611fc5fc2b227a51&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10c3b1cc4c0a5d44aa2c137a52eaf0b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0a00a7bb666b381893da579a6b228c9&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-583182dd35a85d121fe43aee2e3cd0eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e73c8ab3a0b248cdeedb8496a5c6f8a9</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841163</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
