<ns0:edge source="LOGCOM" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC requests coordination and funding from LOGCOM through BICmd for Repair and Return services.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC arranges shipment of downloaded weapons to LOGCOM for maintenance and conducts joint inventories upon return.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC submits Physical Inventory Control Plans in accordance with LOGCOM guidance.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC supports LOGCOM internal testing by fulfilling sample requirements directed from higher headquarters.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">compliance,coordination,funding,internal testing,inventory plan,maintenance coordination,support,weapon handling</ns0:data>
