</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="APSR" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">6.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC adjusts property records in APSR upon Government approval to match on-hand inventory.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC ensures physical inventory matches APSR records and submits recommended adjustments.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC transacts in the APSR, using RPAs for routine tasks and ensuring seamless integration.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC documents all actions on materiel in the APSR to maintain accurate data visibility.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC reconciles acquisitions, dispositions, and inventory results with APSR property records including data elements and adjustments.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC completes APSR transactions for weapons shipped to and received from LOGCOM on the same day as physical actions.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">accountability,adjustment transactions,data transaction,documentation,inventory management,maintenance,reconciliation,record maintenance,system utilization,systems of record,transaction recording</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-67bad1bd73dd9a9a7549acb855ae5e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22de15a10ae9bfba6096cca855d5f78a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-93752a7bd8aca85ef0ce5fea3701dc32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2bae9a24e71825050f79fc141b2e181&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd3a05bb896b89de7fd366c654ad4a6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a0a00a7bb666b381893da579a6b228c9</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841190</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="APSR" target="NIIN">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">NIIN is used in inventory results to identify items for adjustments in APSR property records.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">data element,record correction</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-67bad1bd73dd9a9a7549acb855ae5e55</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841238</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="APSR" target="MPE/S">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC maintains accurate accountability of MPE/S within APSR through physical inventories.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">accountability maintenance,inventory management</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-67bad1bd73dd9a9a7549acb855ae5e55</ns0:data>
