<ns0:edge source="SECREPs" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">3.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC conducts and records operational and serviceability checks on SECREPs in accordance with specified Marine Corps Orders.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC manages sourcing of SECREPs for MMFAU1 to allowance levels, prioritizing least costly methods like lateral support.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC submits GCSS-MC produced SECREPs signed by the RO after production cycles.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">RO endorsement,checking,cost avoidance,listing submission,recording,sourcing management</ns0:data>
