  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC prepares, submits, and follows up on Supply Discrepancy Reports (SDR) for variations in received goods.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC prepares and submits SDRs via PDREP for variations in received goods against documentation.</ns0:data>
