<ns0:edge source="IUID" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">5.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC places and registers IUID tags on items upon receipt at DMO and associates them using MCPIC applications per MCO 4410.28.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC utilizes IUID for asset visibility and management through the DoD IUID Registry.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC places and registers IUID tags on items upon receipt at DMO and registers them in IMARK in accordance with MCPIC Data Standards.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC places and registers IUID tags on items prior to government acceptance per MCO 4410.28.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC applies and registers IUID on equipment using MCPIC to ensure compliance with tracking standards prior to final acceptance.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">application,compliance,identification,registration,tagging,tracking,utilization</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-5fcb066f3ce0c1cfffc65441135b96e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38be7e49aefd10e870f45cb648f7d79d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65833c099ebcc7aa1fccc5a1d930a7aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89b1a9fa6c0722adcd478e665df09141&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f808346dbf233cd47e4c673a7cf87022</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841258</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
