  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">IUID and pRFID tags are associated accurately by the MCMC using MCPIC applications in compliance with MCO 4410.28.&lt;SEP&gt;IUID and pRFID tags are accurately associated using MCPIC per MCO 4410.28.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">association,identification technologies,standardization</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-89b1a9fa6c0722adcd478e665df09141&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f808346dbf233cd47e4c673a7cf87022</ns0:data>
