<ns0:edge source="pRFID" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">3.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC affixes ISO pRFID tags to items and registers them in IMARK prior to government acceptance per MCO 4410.28.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC conducts pRFID PACMAN runs at least twice per week to update equipment and container locations in MCPIC iTRACK.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC applies pRFID tags on all items for identification in compliance with standards.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">location tracking,runs,standards compliance,tagging,tracking</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-5fcb066f3ce0c1cfffc65441135b96e1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89b1a9fa6c0722adcd478e665df09141&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f808346dbf233cd47e4c673a7cf87022</ns0:data>
