<ns0:edge source="MMC" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC applies fresh lubricant to ME and CESE during designated MMC production periods after final rinse and prior to staging.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC conducts various logistics operations including inventories and packing during the MMC production period.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC develops plans and procures materiel to support MMC production and sustainment operations.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC executes tasks for MMC including 120 Day Pre-MMC reporting, equipment offload requirements, and maintenance transfers.</ns0:data>
