<ns0:edge source="MCO 4790.2" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">3.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC complies with MCO 4790.2 for requisition validations, receipt processing, and SECREP handling.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC adheres to MCO 4790.2 for inputting data into AIS, conducting validations, establishing calibration and modification programs, maintaining equipment records, and executing training.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC establishes and executes Training Program in accordance with MCO 4790.2.</ns0:data>
