  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC submits Supply Discrepancy Reports (SDR) and conducts receipt validations according to SECNAVINST 4355.18 timelines.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC submits Supply Discrepancy Reports in accordance with timelines in SECNAVINST 4355.18.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC follows SECNAVINST 4355.18 for timelines in preparing and following up on Supply Discrepancy Reports.</ns0:data>
