<ns0:edge source="Unliquidated Obligations (ULO)" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">3.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC performs validations of Unliquidated Obligations to ensure proper handling of obligations and de-obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC completes validations of Unliquidated Obligations (ULO) to align with receipts and requisitions.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC conducts receipt validations including reconciliation against Unliquidated Obligations (ULO) to manage obligations and de-obligations.</ns0:data>
