  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC complies with DoD 8140 for annual IA certifications under the Cybersecurity Workforce program.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC IT support positions comply with DoD 8140 requirements for Information Assurance Workforce level II technical certifications.</ns0:data>
