<ns0:edge source="Section 11.A" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Section 11.A assigns MCMC responsibilities for Help Desk operations, scheduled and unscheduled support, audio/visual systems, and consumable supplies inventory.&lt;SEP&gt;Section 11.A mandates the MCMC's responsibilities for scheduled and emergency after-hours and weekend maintenance support.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">help desk operations,maintenance,support requirements</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-cf666a8ded534eb47b7eede4412a01f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-789ddbe0005097425aa3559f9388ad80</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841179</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="Section 11.B" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Section 11.B directs MCMC to install authorized hardware and software, maintain accountability, and comply with STIGs and DADMS.&lt;SEP&gt;Section 11.B requires the MCMC to perform installations and maintain accountability of hardware and software.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">accountability,installation</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-cf666a8ded534eb47b7eede4412a01f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-789ddbe0005097425aa3559f9388ad80</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841180</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="Section 11.C" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Section 11.C requires MCMC to perform maintenance on hardware, document in GCSS-MC, conduct preventive maintenance per CmdO 2620.1, and report failures to S-6.&lt;SEP&gt;Section 11.C directs the MCMC to conduct preventive maintenance and root cause analysis on hardware.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">hardware maintenance,troubleshooting</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-cf666a8ded534eb47b7eede4412a01f1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-789ddbe0005097425aa3559f9388ad80</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
