<ns0:edge source="MCPP" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC manages portable fire extinguishers centrally for MCPP, developing SOPs for tracking and inspections.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC performs network administration and provides life cycle management recommendations in support of MCPP voice, video, and data systems.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">extinguisher control,operations,program management,support</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-abd2ceb311ce78c8a8c1fe38d11ee4f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-789ddbe0005097425aa3559f9388ad80</ns0:data>
