  <ns0:data key="d7">#&gt;|The MCMC assists ICART with external agency inventory testing and sample responses.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC supports ICART by providing sample responses, Key Supporting Documents, and pictures within five days for APSR validation.</ns0:data>
