  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC processes unserviceable DLRs for one-for-one exchange with DLA after obtaining government approval.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC procures parts through DLA for GSE/GFE unless otherwise approved.</ns0:data>
