  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC provides itemized cost estimates CDRL 6076 and others IAW FAR Subpart 15.4-Contract Pricing within 10 business days.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">compliance,cost estimation</ns0:data>
