  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Navy Watercraft Maintenance Center (WMC) includes LARC Maintenance Facility (LMF) for maintaining LARC program.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">facility support,maintenance program</ns0:data>
