</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="29 CFR 1910" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC complies with 29 CFR 1910 for fire safety, inspections, training, and various safety programs.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC complies with 29 CFR 1910 safety and occupational health requirements IAW Marine Corps Order 5100.29.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">compliance,occupational health,reference</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-48caa545ec007aaf46c9abe9ec8c0c78&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b825754de20bbf2c5befd6a79730280e</ns0:data>
