<ns0:edge source="MCO P3000.17" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC performs surveillance, maintenance, and logistics services in accordance with MCO P3000.17 for Navy equipment during the afloat phase.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC conducts surveillance, maintenance, and logistics services as identified in MCO P3000.17 during Afloat Phase.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">afloat activities,governance compliance,guidance</ns0:data>
