<ns0:edge source="ME" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC performs fuel filtration services on ME assets during designated MMC and MCPP-PHIL production periods in accordance with fuel filtration TM.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC maintains positive chain of custody for ME during shipments and transfers.</ns0:data>
