<ns0:edge source="ME" target="CESE">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">ME and CESE undergo similar corrective maintenance, SL-3 inventory, and modification instructions during production periods.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">corrective actions,shared maintenance</ns0:data>
