  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC replaces lubricity fuel filters on EBFL every 250 hours or 6 months and validates replacements during JLTI.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC replaces lubricity fuel filters on EBFL every 250 hours or 6 months, validating replacements during post-MPS JLTI and recording in GCSS-MC.</ns0:data>
