<ns0:edge source="MPF" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">5.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC ensures materiel loaded on MPF meets minimum shelf life requirements at embarkation.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC manages physical inventories and accountability for equipment and supplies in the MPF program.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC prepares sustainment blocks and manages deficiencies for MPF ship and ashore programs in maintenance cycles.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC supports MPF exercises with supply operations and applies waivers for fire extinguisher inspections during Afloat Phase.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC performs joint inventories of weapons and materiel downloaded from MPF during MMC prior to shipment or storage.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">download,embarkation,exercise support,inventory conduct,joint inventory,production operations,program management,shelf life,support,waiver application</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-abd2ceb311ce78c8a8c1fe38d11ee4f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67bad1bd73dd9a9a7549acb855ae5e55&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22de15a10ae9bfba6096cca855d5f78a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65833c099ebcc7aa1fccc5a1d930a7aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bd3a05bb896b89de7fd366c654ad4a6b</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841266</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="KSDs" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC uploads KSDs into GCSS-MC to support transfers and ensure proper chain of custody.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC uploads KSDs into GCSS-MC for transfers in support of exercises or loans.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">chain of custody,document upload,documentation</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-68739860c42b764e52f9649ea16ed702&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-67bad1bd73dd9a9a7549acb855ae5e55</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841212</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="KSDs" target="Exercise Support Letter">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Exercise Support Letters are included as KSDs for uploading into GCSS-MC to ensure chain of custody.</ns0:data>
