  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC performs inventories and submits the Navy Production Assembly and Class IX Inventory Short List (CDRL 6027) for shortages.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">inventory,shortage identification</ns0:data>
