<ns0:edge source="Planning Consideration Letter (PCL)" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC receipts and distributes Navy weapons and handles containerized equipment per the ship’s Planning Consideration Letter (PCL).</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">compliance,coordination</ns0:data>
