  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC arranges bonded carrier shipments of weapons to LOGCOM in accordance with DTR 4500.9-R Part II.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC conducts transportation management receiving and processes Class V shipments according to DTR 4500.9-R Part II.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">compliance,protective transport,transportation</ns0:data>
