<ns0:edge source="DA Form 2404" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">3.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC retains DA Form 2404 inspection forms for ISO containers until the next inspection.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC submits DA Form 2404 with cost estimates for container repairs to NAV-P.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC retains DA Form 2404 on containers and provides copies to NAV-P.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">approval,inspection,inspection documentation,record keeping,retention,submission</ns0:data>
