<ns0:edge source="ICODES" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC populates IPACK data elements required for ICODES in accordance with MMC Execution Milestones timelines.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC validates and updates ICODES deck diagrams after backload in conjunction with the government.</ns0:data>
