  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC submits Pre-Exercise Status Report on serviceability and open requests for offload equipment.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC submits Pre-Exercise Status Report to assess equipment serviceability and status prior to MCPP-PHIL and ashore exercises.</ns0:data>
