<ns0:edge source="PEDL" target="MCMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC delivers PEDL to document equipment damages after exercises for COR review.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC delivers PEDL detailing equipment damages after exercises and backload operations.</ns0:data>
