  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC performs LTIs on CESE to determine condition, assign codes, and estimate repair costs.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC performs LTI for Navy CESE shipments and submits DD Form 1348-1 and DD Form 1149.</ns0:data>
