<ns0:edge source="MCMC" target="WMC">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC establishes and maintains WMC with dedicated personnel for Navy watercraft maintenance, including LARC and ABLTS.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC conducts hazardous material inventory inspections at WMC and manages waste per 40 CFR.</ns0:data>
