<ns0:edge source="MCMC" target="Portable Fire Extinguishers">
  <ns0:data key="d6">4.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC centrally manages portable fire extinguishers, ensuring NFPA compliance, inspections, and certifications.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC inspects, services, and records serial numbers and storage locations of portable fire extinguishers as SL-3 components in GCSS-MC.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC centrally manages Portable Fire Extinguishers in accordance with NFPA standards.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC maintains annual inventories and conducts monthly inspections of portable fire extinguishers in work areas.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">compliance,inspection,inventory,management,recording</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-13a4841aefad66042f059edb023e607b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-22de15a10ae9bfba6096cca855d5f78a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-abd2ceb311ce78c8a8c1fe38d11ee4f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b825754de20bbf2c5befd6a79730280e</ns0:data>
