<ns0:edge source="MCMC" target="MCSF-BI Temporary Armory Facility">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC utilizes the MCSF-BI Temporary Armory Facility for storing PMCS-completed weapons returning from LOGCOM.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">storage management,weapon security</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-22de15a10ae9bfba6096cca855d5f78a</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d10">M6700425R0007 MCPP II DRAFT RFP 23 MAY 25.pdf</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d11">1759841349</ns0:data>
</ns0:edge>
<ns0:edge source="MCMC" target="Frigard Temporary Armory Facility">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC nominates primary and alternate armory custodians for the Frigard Temporary Armory Facility.&lt;SEP&gt;The MCMC nominates armory custodians and maintains two-person integrity for the Frigard Temporary Armory Facility under MCPP-N.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">access control,custodianship,personnel nomination,security rule</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-22de15a10ae9bfba6096cca855d5f78a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-abd2ceb311ce78c8a8c1fe38d11ee4f4</ns0:data>
