  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC performs equipment maintenance and materiel management primarily at Blount Island facilities.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC performs installation, configuration, administration, operation, and maintenance of voice, video, and data services at Blount Island under S-6 direction.</ns0:data>
