<ns0:edge source="MCMC" target="Quality Meeting">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC participates in Quality Meeting to address six KPIs and planned corrective actions for negative trends.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC participates in the Quality Meeting to review production planning and execution using CEI and SEI.</ns0:data>
