  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC submits inventories, rosters, reports, and notifications to IDIV Safety Office regarding safety equipment and incidents.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC notifies IDIV Safety Office of unsafe situations, submits inventories, and obtains permits for hot work.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">notification,permit coordination,reporting</ns0:data>
