  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC designates and submits the Fire Wardens Roster to identify competent persons for fire emergencies in work areas.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC provides the Fire Wardens Roster annually and within 30 days of personnel changes.</ns0:data>
