<ns0:edge source="MCMC" target="Evacuation Routes">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">MCMC provides initial and updated evacuation routes as maps for government review within specified timelines.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC provides Evacuation Routes as maps for government review to ensure safe egress from work areas.</ns0:data>
