<ns0:edge source="MCMC" target="OSHA">
  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The MCMC complies with OSHA regulations including 29 CFR 1910.95 for hearing conservation and 29 CFR 1910.1200 for hazard communication.&lt;SEP&gt;MCMC complies with OSHA standards across safety programs and submits corrective action reports for citations.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">citations,regulatory compliance</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-fce6cd46a0bc9b7bd7d409339addb37d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b825754de20bbf2c5befd6a79730280e</ns0:data>
