  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Section 4.C.5.b directs use of STRATIS for MMV200 with a warehouse denial rate not exceeding 2%.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">denial rate limit,system utilization</ns0:data>
