  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Section 4.C.5.c requires establishment of COSIS program with plan submission within 60 days and annually.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">annual submission,program establishment</ns0:data>
