  <ns0:data key="d7">The Memorandum of Understanding Governing Pre-Stockage and Reinforcement of Norway establishes the legal basis for maintaining and reinforcing prepositioned assets in the Marine Corps Prepositioning Program – Norway.</ns0:data>
