  <ns0:data key="d7">Small Business Subcontracting Plan covers Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Businesses to meet the 1% goal.&lt;SEP&gt;Small Business Subcontracting Plan sets a 1% goal for Service-Disabled Veteran-Owned Small Business concerns.</ns0:data>
