<ns0:edge source="Statement of Work" target="Volume III">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Volume III methodologies for supply, maintenance, and manning comply with Statement of Work sections C.4, C.2.B, C.3, and attachments like C.1-7.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">USMC operations,methodology alignment</ns0:data>
