  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">Technical Capability is one of the areas investigated in the L-3 pre-award survey to determine contractor performance ability.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">capability assessment,evaluation area</ns0:data>
