  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">KPIs for Program Management Effectiveness are derived from business systems including the PPC tool used by the MCMC.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">performance derivation,system integration</ns0:data>
