  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">GSA Leased Vehicles receive maintenance and repair support under the broader NTVE maintenance requirements.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">repair coordination,support integration</ns0:data>
