<ns0:edge source="Naval Construction Element (NCE)" target="Marine Prepositioning Force (MPF)">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">NCE equipment, including rotational spares and designated management stock, supports the Marine Prepositioning Force (MPF) Program.</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d8">equipment assignment,program support</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d9">chunk-a9aba44b05f751488f4a50faebf206cb</ns0:data>
