  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">52.216-7 Allowable Cost And Payment requires reconciliation of total payroll per Irs Form 941 to total labor costs distribution in indirect cost proposals.</ns0:data>
