  <ns0:data key="d6">2.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">DFARS 215.304 provides criteria for evaluating Small Business Participation Proposal.&lt;SEP&gt;Small Business Participation Proposal is evaluated per DFARS 215.304, weighting enforceable commitments more heavily.</ns0:data>
