<ns0:edge source="52.222-42 Statement of Equivalent Rates for Federal Hires" target="Service Employee Classes">
  <ns0:data key="d6">1.0</ns0:data>
  <ns0:data key="d7">The statement identifies service employee classes and specifies equivalent wages and fringe benefits payable under 5 U.S.C. 5341 or 5332.</ns0:data>
